  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Researchers are assessing whether use of a virtual reality experience, used during the
      procedure, can reduce anxiety and improve satisfaction related to the procedure, especially
      when no or little sedation is being used.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
